definitions.definition: The largest department in the Nouvelle-Aquitaine region, France .
An estuary in the Nouvelle-Aquitaine region, France , formed by the merger of the rivers Garonne and Dordogne ; in full, the Gironde estuary .

main_definition: The largest department in the Nouvelle-Aquitaine region, France .
